echnical_Reference.html:84:<header id=\"title-block-header\">\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:87:<h1 id=\"feddsa-技术参考手册\">FedDSA 技术参考手册</h1>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:88:<h2 id=\"一网络架构\">一、网络架构</h2>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:89:<h3 id=\"整体架构图\">1.1 整体架构图</h3>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:134:<h3 id=\"各模块维度\">1.2 各模块维度</h3>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:183:<h3 id=\"为什么这样设计聚合策略\">1.3 为什么这样设计聚合策略</h3>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:191:<h2 id=\"二三大核心模块\">二、三大核心模块</h2>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:192:<h3 id=\"decouple-解耦\">2.1 Decouple (解耦)</h3>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:194:<h4 id=\"正交约束-l_orth\">正交约束 L_orth</h4>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:195:<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb3\"><pre class=\"sourceCode python\"><code class=\"sourceCode python\"><span id=\"cb3-1\"><a href=\"#cb3-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>z_sem_n <span class=\"op\">=</span> F.normalize(z_sem, dim<span class=\"op\">=</span><span class=\"dv\">1</span>)  <span class=\"co\"># L2归一化</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:196:<span id=\"cb3-2\"><a href=\"#cb3-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>z_sty_n <span class=\"op\">=</span> F.normalize(z_sty, dim<span class=\"op\">=</span><span class=\"dv\">1</span>)  <span class=\"co\"># L2归一化</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:197:<span id=\"cb3-3\"><a href=\"#cb3-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>cos <span class=\"op\">=</span> (z_sem_n <span class=\"op\">*</span> z_sty_n).<span class=\"bu\">sum</span>(dim<span class=\"op\">=</span><span class=\"dv\">1</span>) <span class=\"co\"># 逐样本余弦相似度 [B]</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:198:<span id=\"cb3-4\"><a href=\"#cb3-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>loss_orth <span class=\"op\">=</span> (cos <span class=\"op\">**</span> <span class=\"dv\">2</span>).mean()         <span class=\"co\"># 平方后取均值</span></span></code></pre></div>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:202:<h4 id=\"hsic-核独立性约束-l_hsic\">HSIC 核独立性约束 L_hsic</h4>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:203:<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb5\"><pre class=\"sourceCode python\"><code class=\"sourceCode python\"><span id=\"cb5-1\"><a href=\"#cb5-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"kw\">def</span> _hsic(<span class=\"va\">self</span>, x, y):</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:204:<span id=\"cb5-2\"><a href=\"#cb5-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    n <span class=\"op\">=</span> x.size(<span class=\"dv\">0</span>)</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:205:<span id=\"cb5-3\"><a href=\"#cb5-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    Kx <span class=\"op\">=</span> gaussian_kernel(x)  <span class=\"co\"># 高斯核矩阵 [n, n]</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:206:<span id=\"cb5-4\"><a href=\"#cb5-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    Ky <span class=\"op\">=</span> gaussian_kernel(y)  <span class=\"co\"># 高斯核矩阵 [n, n]</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:207:<span id=\"cb5-5\"><a href=\"#cb5-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    H <span class=\"op\">=</span> I <span class=\"op\">-</span> (<span class=\"dv\">1</span><span class=\"op\">/</span>n) <span class=\"op\">*</span> <span class=\"dv\">11</span><span class=\"op\">^</span>T     <span class=\"co\"># 中心化矩阵</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:208:<span id=\"cb5-6\"><a href=\"#cb5-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"cf\">return</span> trace(Kx <span class=\"op\">@</span> H <span class=\"op\">@</span> Ky <span class=\"op\">@</span> H) <span class=\"op\">/</span> n<span class=\"op\">^</span><span class=\"dv\">2</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:209:<span id=\"cb5-7\"><a href=\"#cb5-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:210:<span id=\"cb5-8\"><a href=\"#cb5-8\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"kw\">def</span> gaussian_kernel(x):</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:211:<span id=\"cb5-9\"><a href=\"#cb5-9\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    dist <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"op\">||</span>x_i <span class=\"op\">-</span> x_j<span class=\"op\">||^</span><span class=\"dv\">2</span>        <span class=\"co\"># 欧氏距离平方矩阵</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:212:<span id=\"cb5-10\"><a href=\"#cb5-10\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    median <span class=\"op\">=</span> median(dist[dist<span class=\"op\">&gt;</span><span class=\"dv\">0</span>])  <span class=\"co\"># 中位数带宽</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:213:<span id=\"cb5-11\"><a href=\"#cb5-11\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    bw <span class=\"op\">=</span> median <span class=\"op\">/</span> (<span class=\"dv\">2</span> <span class=\"op\">*</span> log(n<span class=\"op\">+</span><span class=\"dv\">1</span>))   <span class=\"co\"># 自适应带宽</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:214:<span id=\"cb5-12\"><a href=\"#cb5-12\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"cf\">return</span> exp(<span class=\"op\">-</span>dist <span class=\"op\">/</span> (<span class=\"dv\">2</span> <span class=\"op\">*</span> bw))   <span class=\"co\"># 高斯核</span></span></code></pre></div>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:216:<h3 id=\"share-风格共享\">2.2 Share (风格共享)</h3>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:218:<h4 id=\"风格仓库收集\">风格仓库收集</h4>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:219:<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb6\"><pre class=\"sourceCode python\"><code class=\"sourceCode python\"><span id=\"cb6-1\"><a href=\"#cb6-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"co\"># 每轮训练结束后, 客户端上传 h 空间的统计量</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:220:<span id=\"cb6-2\"><a href=\"#cb6-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>mu <span class=\"op\">=</span> style_sum <span class=\"op\">/</span> style_n           <span class=\"co\"># h 在 batch 维度的均值 [1024]</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:221:<span id=\"cb6-3\"><a href=\"#cb6-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>var <span class=\"op\">=</span> style_sq_sum <span class=\"op\">/</span> style_n <span class=\"op\">-</span> mu<span class=\"op\">^</span><span class=\"dv\">2</span>  <span class=\"co\"># 方差 = E[X^2] - (E[X])^2</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:222:<span id=\"cb6-4\"><a href=\"#cb6-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>sigma <span class=\"op\">=</span> sqrt(var.clamp(<span class=\"bu\">min</span><span class=\"op\">=</span><span class=\"fl\">1e-6</span>))    <span class=\"co\"># 标准差 [1024]</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:223:<span id=\"cb6-5\"><a href=\"#cb6-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:224:<span id=\"cb6-6\"><a href=\"#cb6-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"co\"># 服务器保存: style_bank[client_id] = (mu, sigma)</span></span></code></pre></div>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:226:<h4 id=\"adain-风格增强-原版-feddsa\">AdaIN 风格增强 (原版 FedDSA)</h4>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:227:<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb7\"><pre class=\"sourceCode python\"><code class=\"sourceCode python\"><span id=\"cb7-1\"><a href=\"#cb7-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"kw\">def</span> _style_augment(<span class=\"va\">self</span>, h):</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:228:<span id=\"cb7-2\"><a href=\"#cb7-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"co\"># 1. 从风格仓库随机取一个外域的 (mu, sigma)</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:229:<span id=\"cb7-3\"><a href=\"#cb7-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    mu_ext, sigma_ext <span class=\"op\">=</span> random_pick(style_bank)  <span class=\"co\"># [1024] each</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:230:<span id=\"cb7-4\"><a href=\"#cb7-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:231:<span id=\"cb7-5\"><a href=\"#cb7-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"co\"># 2. 计算本地 batch 的统计量</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:232:<span id=\"cb7-6\"><a href=\"#cb7-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    mu_local <span class=\"op\">=</span> h.mean(dim<span class=\"op\">=</span><span class=\"dv\">0</span>)                      <span class=\"co\"># [1024]</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:233:<span id=\"cb7-7\"><a href=\"#cb7-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    sigma_local <span class=\"op\">=</span> h.std(dim<span class=\"op\">=</span><span class=\"dv\">0</span>).clamp(<span class=\"bu\">min</span><span class=\"op\">=</span><span class=\"fl\">1e-6</span>)    <span class=\"co\"># [1024]</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:234:<span id=\"cb7-8\"><a href=\"#cb7-8\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:235:<span id=\"cb7-9\"><a href=\"#cb7-9\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"co\"># 3. 随机混合强度</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:236:<span id=\"cb7-10\"><a href=\"#cb7-10\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    alpha <span class=\"op\">=</span> np.random.beta(<span class=\"fl\">0.1</span>, <span class=\"fl\">0.1</span>)  <span class=\"co\"># U形分布, 多数为0或1</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:237:<span id=\"cb7-11\"><a href=\"#cb7-11\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:238:<span id=\"cb7-12\"><a href=\"#cb7-12\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"co\"># 4. 混合统计量</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:239:<span id=\"cb7-13\"><a href=\"#cb7-13\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    mu_mix <span class=\"op\">=</span> alpha <span class=\"op\">*</span> mu_local <span class=\"op\">+</span> (<span class=\"dv\">1</span><span class=\"op\">-</span>alpha) <span class=\"op\">*</span> mu_ext</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:240:<span id=\"cb7-14\"><a href=\"#cb7-14\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    sigma_mix <span class=\"op\">=</span> alpha <span class=\"op\">*</span> sigma_local <span class=\"op\">+</span> (<span class=\"dv\">1</span><span class=\"op\">-</span>alpha) <span class=\"op\">*</span> sigma_ext</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:241:<span id=\"cb7-15\"><a href=\"#cb7-15\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:242:<span id=\"cb7-16\"><a href=\"#cb7-16\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"co\"># 5. AdaIN: 去掉本地风格, 穿上混合风格</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:243:<span id=\"cb7-17\"><a href=\"#cb7-17\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    h_norm <span class=\"op\">=</span> (h <span class=\"op\">-</span> mu_local) <span class=\"op\">/</span> sigma_local    <span class=\"co\"># 标准化 → 纯内容</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:244:<span id=\"cb7-18\"><a href=\"#cb7-18\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    h_aug <span class=\"op\">=</span> h_norm <span class=\"op\">*</span> sigma_mix <span class=\"op\">+</span> mu_mix       <span class=\"co\"># 上色 → 混合风格</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:245:<span id=\"cb7-19\"><a href=\"#cb7-19\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"cf\">return</span> h_aug  <span class=\"co\"># [B, 1024]</span></span></code></pre></div>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:262:<h3 id=\"align-语义对齐\">2.3 Align (语义对齐)</h3>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:264:<h4 id=\"全局原型的收集\">全局原型的收集</h4>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:265:<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb9\"><pre class=\"sourceCode python\"><code class=\"sourceCode python\"><span id=\"cb9-1\"><a href=\"#cb9-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"co\"># 客户端: 在最后一个 epoch, 按类聚合 z_sem</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:266:<span id=\"cb9-2\"><a href=\"#cb9-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"cf\">for</span> each sample (z_sem_i, y_i):</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:267:<span id=\"cb9-3\"><a href=\"#cb9-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    proto_sum[y_i] <span class=\"op\">+=</span> z_sem_i</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:268:<span id=\"cb9-4\"><a href=\"#cb9-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    proto_count[y_i] <span class=\"op\">+=</span> <span class=\"dv\">1</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:269:<span id=\"cb9-5\"><a href=\"#cb9-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>local_proto[c] <span class=\"op\">=</span> proto_sum[c] <span class=\"op\">/</span> proto_count[c]  <span class=\"co\"># 每类一个 [128] 向量</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:270:<span id=\"cb9-6\"><a href=\"#cb9-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:271:<span id=\"cb9-7\"><a href=\"#cb9-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"co\"># 服务器: 加权平均所有客户端的同类原型</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:272:<span id=\"cb9-8\"><a href=\"#cb9-8\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>global_proto[c] <span class=\"op\">=</span> weighted_mean(all_clients_proto[c])</span></code></pre></div>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:273:<h4 id=\"infonce-对比损失\">InfoNCE 对比损失</h4>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:274:<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb10\"><pre class=\"sourceCode python\"><code class=\"sourceCode python\"><span id=\"cb10-1\"><a href=\"#cb10-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"kw\">def</span> _infonce_loss(<span class=\"va\">self</span>, z_sem, y):</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:275:<span id=\"cb10-2\"><a href=\"#cb10-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"co\"># proto_matrix: 所有类的全局原型 [C, 128], C=类别数(如7)</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:276:<span id=\"cb10-3\"><a href=\"#cb10-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    proto_matrix <span class=\"op\">=</span> stack([global_proto[c] <span class=\"cf\">for</span> c <span class=\"kw\">in</span> classes])</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:277:<span id=\"cb10-4\"><a href=\"#cb10-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:278:<span id=\"cb10-5\"><a href=\"#cb10-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"co\"># L2 归一化</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:279:<span id=\"cb10-6\"><a href=\"#cb10-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    z_n <span class=\"op\">=</span> normalize(z_sem)     <span class=\"co\"># [B, 128]</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:280:<span id=\"cb10-7\"><a href=\"#cb10-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    p_n <span class=\"op\">=</span> normalize(proto_matrix) <span class=\"co\"># [C, 128]</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:281:<span id=\"cb10-8\"><a href=\"#cb10-8\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:282:<span id=\"cb10-9\"><a href=\"#cb10-9\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"co\"># 计算相似度矩阵 / 温度</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:283:<span id=\"cb10-10\"><a href=\"#cb10-10\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    logits <span class=\"op\">=</span> (z_n <span class=\"op\">@</span> p_n.T) <span class=\"op\">/</span> tau  <span class=\"co\"># [B, C]</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:284:<span id=\"cb10-11\"><a href=\"#cb10-11\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:285:<span id=\"cb10-12\"><a href=\"#cb10-12\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"co\"># 交叉熵: 每个样本的正确类别应得到最高 logit</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:286:<span id=\"cb10-13\"><a href=\"#cb10-13\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    loss <span class=\"op\">=</span> cross_entropy(logits, y)</span></code></pre></div>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:296:<h2 id=\"三总损失函数\">三、总损失函数</h2>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:297:<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb12\"><pre class=\"sourceCode python\"><code class=\"sourceCode python\"><span id=\"cb12-1\"><a href=\"#cb12-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>L_total <span class=\"op\">=</span> L_CE(z_sem, y)                        <span class=\"co\"># 任务损失</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:298:<span id=\"cb12-2\"><a href=\"#cb12-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        <span class=\"op\">+</span> L_CE(z_sem_aug, y)                     <span class=\"co\"># 增强后任务损失</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:299:<span id=\"cb12-3\"><a href=\"#cb12-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        <span class=\"op\">+</span> w <span class=\"op\">*</span> lambda_orth <span class=\"op\">*</span> L_orth               <span class=\"co\"># 正交解耦</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:300:<span id=\"cb12-4\"><a href=\"#cb12-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        <span class=\"op\">+</span> w <span class=\"op\">*</span> lambda_hsic <span class=\"op\">*</span> L_HSIC               <span class=\"co\"># 核独立性</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:301:<span id=\"cb12-5\"><a href=\"#cb12-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        <span class=\"op\">+</span> w <span class=\"op\">*</span> lambda_sem  <span class=\"op\">*</span> L_InfoNCE            <span class=\"co\"># 语义对齐</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:302:<span id=\"cb12-6\"><a href=\"#cb12-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:303:<span id=\"cb12-7\"><a href=\"#cb12-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>其中 w <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"bu\">min</span>(<span class=\"fl\">1.0</span>, current_round <span class=\"op\">/</span> warmup_rounds)  <span class=\"co\"># warmup 权重</span></span></code></pre></div>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:314:<h2 id=\"四adaptive-改进-feddsa_adaptive.py\">四、Adaptive 改进 (feddsa_adaptive.py)</h2>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:315:<h3 id=\"m1-自适应增强强度\">4.1 M1: 自适应增强强度</h3>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:318:<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb14\"><pre class=\"sourceCode python\"><code class=\"sourceCode python\"><span id=\"cb14-1\"><a href=\"#cb14-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"co\"># --- 服务器端: 计算 gap ---</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:319:<span id=\"cb14-2\"><a href=\"#cb14-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"co\"># 收集各客户端 z_sty 的 (mu, sigma) (不是 h 的!)</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:320:<span id=\"cb14-3\"><a href=\"#cb14-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"cf\">for</span> each client i:</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:321:<span id=\"cb14-4\"><a href=\"#cb14-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    raw_gap[i] <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"op\">||</span>mu_zsty_i <span class=\"op\">-</span> mu_zsty_global<span class=\"op\">||^</span><span class=\"dv\">2</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:322:<span id=\"cb14-5\"><a href=\"#cb14-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>               <span class=\"op\">+</span> <span class=\"op\">||</span>sigma_zsty_i <span class=\"op\">-</span> sigma_zsty_global<span class=\"op\">||^</span><span class=\"dv\">2</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:323:<span id=\"cb14-6\"><a href=\"#cb14-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:324:<span id=\"cb14-7\"><a href=\"#cb14-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"co\"># EMA z-score 归一化</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:325:<span id=\"cb14-8\"><a href=\"#cb14-8\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>mean_gap, std_gap <span class=\"op\">=</span> EMA_update(mean_gap, std_gap, gaps)</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:326:<span id=\"cb14-9\"><a href=\"#cb14-9\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>z_score[i] <span class=\"op\">=</span> (raw_gap[i] <span class=\"op\">-</span> mean_gap) <span class=\"op\">/</span> std_gap</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:327:<span id=\"cb14-10\"><a href=\"#cb14-10\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>gap_normalized[i] <span class=\"op\">=</span> clip(z_score <span class=\"op\">*</span> <span class=\"fl\">0.5</span> <span class=\"op\">+</span> <span class=\"fl\">0.5</span>, <span class=\"dv\">0</span>, <span class=\"dv\">1</span>)</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:328:<span id=\"cb14-11\"><a href=\"#cb14-11\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:329:<span id=\"cb14-12\"><a href=\"#cb14-12\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"co\"># --- 客户端端: 自适应 alpha ---</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:330:<span id=\"cb14-13\"><a href=\"#cb14-13\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>alpha <span class=\"op\">=</span> aug_min <span class=\"op\">+</span> (aug_max <span class=\"op\">-</span> aug_min) <span class=\"op\">*</span> gap_normalized <span class=\"op\">+</span> N(<span class=\"dv\">0</span>, noise_std)</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:331:<span id=\"cb14-14\"><a href=\"#cb14-14\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>alpha <span class=\"op\">=</span> clip(alpha, aug_min, aug_max)</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:332:<span id=\"cb14-15\"><a href=\"#cb14-15\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:333:<span id=\"cb14-16\"><a href=\"#cb14-16\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"co\"># AdaIN 增强 (不同于原版!)</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:334:<span id=\"cb14-17\"><a href=\"#cb14-17\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>h_adain <span class=\"op\">=</span> h_norm <span class=\"op\">*</span> sigma_ext <span class=\"op\">+</span> mu_ext     <span class=\"co\"># 完整风格迁移</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:335:<span id=\"cb14-18\"><a href=\"#cb14-18\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>h_aug <span class=\"op\">=</span> alpha <span class=\"op\">*</span> h_adain <span class=\"op\">+</span> (<span class=\"dv\">1</span><span class=\"op\">-</span>alpha) <span class=\"op\">*</span> h   <span class=\"co\"># 按 alpha 比例混合</span></span></code></pre></div>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:343:<h3 id=\"m3-域感知原型对齐\">4.2 M3: 域感知原型对齐</h3>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:345:<p><strong>改进</strong>: 保留 (class, client_id) 独立原型, 用 SupCon InfoNCE。</p>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:346:<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb16\"><pre class=\"sourceCode python\"><code class=\"sourceCode python\"><span id=\"cb16-1\"><a href=\"#cb16-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"co\"># --- 服务器端: 存储域级原型 ---</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:347:<span id=\"cb16-2\"><a href=\"#cb16-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>domain_protos <span class=\"op\">=</span> {}</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:348:<span id=\"cb16-3\"><a href=\"#cb16-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"cf\">for</span> client_id, protos <span class=\"kw\">in</span> all_client_protos:</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:349:<span id=\"cb16-4\"><a href=\"#cb16-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"cf\">for</span> class_c, proto <span class=\"kw\">in</span> protos:</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:350:<span id=\"cb16-5\"><a href=\"#cb16-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>        domain_protos[(class_c, client_id)] <span class=\"op\">=</span> proto</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:351:<span id=\"cb16-6\"><a href=\"#cb16-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"co\"># 例: domain_protos = {</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:352:<span id=\"cb16-7\"><a href=\"#cb16-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"co\">#   (dog, Photo): [128d], (dog, Art): [128d],</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:353:<span id=\"cb16-8\"><a href=\"#cb16-8\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"co\">#   (dog, Cartoon): [128d], (dog, Sketch): [128d],</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:354:<span id=\"cb16-9\"><a href=\"#cb16-9\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"co\">#   (cat, Photo): [128d], ... }</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:355:<span id=\"cb16-10\"><a href=\"#cb16-10\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:356:<span id=\"cb16-11\"><a href=\"#cb16-11\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"co\"># --- 客户端端: SupCon Multi-Positive InfoNCE ---</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:357:<span id=\"cb16-12\"><a href=\"#cb16-12\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>proto_matrix <span class=\"op\">=</span> stack(<span class=\"bu\">all</span> domain_protos)  <span class=\"co\"># [N_total, 128]</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:358:<span id=\"cb16-13\"><a href=\"#cb16-13\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>proto_labels <span class=\"op\">=</span> [<span class=\"kw\">class</span> <span class=\"cf\">for</span> (<span class=\"kw\">class</span>, cid) <span class=\"kw\">in</span> keys]</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:359:<span id=\"cb16-14\"><a href=\"#cb16-14\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:360:<span id=\"cb16-15\"><a href=\"#cb16-15\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>z_n <span class=\"op\">=</span> normalize(z_sem)</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:361:<span id=\"cb16-16\"><a href=\"#cb16-16\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>p_n <span class=\"op\">=</span> normalize(proto_matrix)</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:362:<span id=\"cb16-17\"><a href=\"#cb16-17\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>logits <span class=\"op\">=</span> z_n <span class=\"op\">@</span> p_n.T <span class=\"op\">/</span> tau  <span class=\"co\"># [B, N_total]</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:363:<span id=\"cb16-18\"><a href=\"#cb16-18\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:364:<span id=\"cb16-19\"><a href=\"#cb16-19\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"co\"># 对每个样本: 同类的所有域原型都是正样本</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:365:<span id=\"cb16-20\"><a href=\"#cb16-20\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"cf\">for</span> sample i <span class=\"cf\">with</span> label y_i:</span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:366:<span id=\"cb16-21\"><a href=\"#cb16-21\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    positives <span class=\"op\">=</span> {j : proto_labels[j] <span class=\"op\">==</span> y_i}  <span class=\"co\"># 可能有 4 个 (4个域)</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:367:<span id=\"cb16-22\"><a href=\"#cb16-22\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    loss_i <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"op\">-</span>(<span class=\"dv\">1</span><span class=\"op\">/|</span>P<span class=\"op\">|</span>) <span class=\"op\">*</span> sum_{p <span class=\"kw\">in</span> positives} log(exp(logits[i,p]) <span class=\"op\">/</span> sum_j exp(logits[i,j]))</span></code></pre></div>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:375:<h3 id=\"实验模式\">4.3 实验模式</h3>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:423:<h2 id=\"五完整超参数表\">五、完整超参数表</h2>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:424:<h3 id=\"核心训练超参数\">5.1 核心训练超参数</h3>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:494:<h3 id=\"feddsa-损失权重\">5.2 FedDSA 损失权重</h3>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:543:<h3 id=\"风格共享参数\">5.3 风格共享参数</h3>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:568:<h3 id=\"adaptive-专用参数\">5.4 Adaptive 专用参数</h3>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:617:<h3 id=\"algo_para-配置格式\">5.5 algo_para 配置格式</h3>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:618:<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb18\"><pre class=\"sourceCode yaml\"><code class=\"sourceCode yaml\"><span id=\"cb18-1\"><a href=\"#cb18-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"co\"># 原版 FedDSA (7 个参数)</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:619:<span id=\"cb18-2\"><a href=\"#cb18-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"fu\">algo_para</span><span class=\"kw\">:</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:620:<span id=\"cb18-3\"><a href=\"#cb18-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"kw\">-</span><span class=\"at\"> </span><span class=\"fl\">1.0</span><span class=\"co\">    # [0] lambda_orth</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:621:<span id=\"cb18-4\"><a href=\"#cb18-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"kw\">-</span><span class=\"at\"> </span><span class=\"fl\">0.0</span><span class=\"co\">    # [1] lambda_hsic</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:622:<span id=\"cb18-5\"><a href=\"#cb18-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"kw\">-</span><span class=\"at\"> </span><span class=\"fl\">1.0</span><span class=\"co\">    # [2] lambda_sem</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:623:<span id=\"cb18-6\"><a href=\"#cb18-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"kw\">-</span><span class=\"at\"> </span><span class=\"fl\">0.2</span><span class=\"co\">    # [3] tau</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:624:<span id=\"cb18-7\"><a href=\"#cb18-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"kw\">-</span><span class=\"at\"> </span><span class=\"dv\">50</span><span class=\"co\">     # [4] warmup_rounds</span></span>\r\n.\\experiments\\FedDSA_Technical_Reference.html:625:<span id=\"cb18-8\"><a href=\"#cb18-8\" aria-hidd